Version History
***************

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 5.5

        @{b}*@{ub} Opens locale.library(38) to work on OS3.0.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 5.4

        @{b}*@{ub} Allow spaces in node names.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version beta1 5.3

        @{b}*@{ub} Recompiled using SAS/C 6.57.

        @{b}*@{ub} Localised.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 5.2

        @{b}*@{ub} Word list resyncs when Search gadget reactivated with one
          word.

        @{b}*@{ub} Changed the file format.

        @{b}*@{ub} Reduced memory usage.

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 5.1

        @{b}*@{ub} Updated Bugs

   @{b}*@{ub} Version 5.0

        @{b}*@{ub} First Version released


@EndNode

